Splendid Medien AG's Subsidiary Signs Contract with Amazon.com On Line Video Store's LOVEFiLM
Monday, 6 Aug 2012 05:01am EDT
Splendid Medien AG announced that its subsidiary Splendid Film GmbH has signed the SVoD (Subscription Video On Demand) contract with LOVEFiLM, Amazon.com's on line video store. From now on the LOVEFiLM's customers in Germany will have for retrieval movie classics and newer movies from the Splendid film library. Moreover, the LOVEFiLM's members with a loan package, will be able to see at any time the Splendid film library, including video-on-demand. The video-on-demand service will work on LOVEFiLM Player on the PC, on Internet-enabled Sony Bravia TVs and on PlayStation3. In addiction with the LOVEFiLM App the movies can be streamed directly to the iPad. Further financial details were not disclosed.Â 
